name: time wasted chasing memories i never knew existed

metadata.name: A Fading Self Reflection
metadata.description:
my day to day life has been shit for atleast 5 years now and all I’ve done is get high everyday and make art to distract myself, having Asperger’s and ADHD it’s been really easy to fall into a never ending cycle, and time has flown by with not much memory of any of it, Ive severely neglected myself and let everything get to such a bad point while never stepping up and taking action to better myself and my life, looking back is fucked up and I wouldn’t wish this on anyone, this piece reflects exactly how I feel.

Manchester 2022.
